  "guru_bin": {
    "retreat": "OSTINATO — Transcendental Vol 1",
    "retreat_date": "2026-03-19",
    "scripture": [
      "Taoist teaching: 'The ten thousand sounds return to the one — the one is silence'",
      "Confucius, Analects: 'Music produces a kind of pleasure which human nature cannot do without'",
      "Daoism, Tao Te Ching 11: 'Thirty spokes share the hub of a wheel; it is the center hole that makes it useful' — the silence between the tongue drum strikes"
    ],
    "revelation": "The Eye discovered: the minor pentatonic in Ostinato is (-3, 2, 4, 9) — a minor pentatonic displaced by a minor third. These intervals (b7, 2, 3, 6 relative to root) create an ambiguous modal sound that is neither sad nor happy but deeply reflective. No pattern matches exactly — the melodic result is emergent from the rhythm pattern interactions.",
    "god": "Eye",
    "flock_note": "The Feather noted: slight swing (0.1) on melodic percussion is the difference between a music box and a human musician. The Log Drum bass voice (tuned -7st) grounds the floating melodic content and creates the garden's 'earth' beneath the 'branches'.",
    "diagnosis": "Tongue Drum Garden II proves that percussion can be a melodic instrument when tuning is treated as sacred — each semitone choice is a garden decision."
  },
